Class SocketPerformancePreferences

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.logging.log4j.core.net.SocketPerformancePreferences
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, Supplier<SocketPerformancePreferences>, org.apache.logging.log4j.plugins.util.Builder<SocketPerformancePreferences>
    @Configurable(printObject=true)
@Plugin
public class SocketPerformancePreferences
extends Object
implements org.apache.logging.log4j.plugins.util.Builder<SocketPerformancePreferences>, Cloneable
    Holds all socket options settable via Socket.setPerformancePreferences(int, int, int).

    The Socket.setPerformancePreferences(int, int, int) API may not be implemented by a JRE.
